&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rusty’s Retirement is an idle farming simulator developed and published by Mister Morris Games. It was released on April 26, 2024 for PC (Windows and Mac). Uniquely, the game is designed to run as a small window at the bottom (or side) of your screen, allowing you to play it while engaging in other activities on your computer.&lt;/p&gt;</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hanifnaoh.com/posts/rusty-and-the-reborn-of-widget/featured.jpg"/></item></channel></rss>